Objectively Funny¶

Adventures in Comedy AI¶

Yuqing Wang, Catriona Beamish, James Farrell, Reinis Melbardis

11/03/2022, London, UK

Problem Statement¶

😃 Comedy is nuanced and a highly "human" thing.

📚 Can we gain insight into how humour is created through natural language processing?

🧠 Can artificial brains be funny?

📜 Data¶

Scraps From the Loft - Full Scripts of Stand-up specials - scripts and year

Subsaga - Live from the BBC, Live at the Apollo and Full Scripts - scripts

The Movie Database (TMDB) - artist age and gender

Project Outcomes¶

🎯 We focussed on two goals:

  • Analysis of common topics and words in stand-up comedy
  • Training an AI to write stand-up, with hilarious consequences
